r, shackle”), as well as رَفّ (raff, “shelf, a part of furniture where one rows things into”), and صُفَّة (ṣuffa, “bench”) is also a borrowing and possibly related to the root."}, "ipa": ["/sˤaff/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n24406", "headword_ar": "صَفٌّ", "root": "Sf", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A rank, row,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "line"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[of things]; (KL, PS;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an even"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sador", "text_ar": "صَدْر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "front,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fore part,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] of any things: (M:) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a company of men standing in a rank,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "row,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "line:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SufuwfN", "text_ar": "صُفُوفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, M, O, Msb, K;) and the sing. may also be used in the sense of the pl.; it may be used either thus in the sense of the pl. or as a sing. in the Kur xviii. 46. (O.) Hence, in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saw~uwA Sufuwfakumo", "text_ar": "سَوُّوا صُفُوفَكُمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Make even your ranks"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] in prayer. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A station of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sufuwf", "text_ar": "صُفُوف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ranks of men"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (M. [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maSaf~N", "text_ar": "مَصَفٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]) And hence, (M,) as used in the Kur xx. 67,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muSal~FY", "text_ar": "مُصَلًّى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A place of prayer,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a place of prayer on the occasion of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eiyd", "text_ar": "عِيد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "festival"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (Az, M, O;) because the people stand there in ranks: (M:) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a place where people assemble for their"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eiyd", "text_ar": "عِيد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Az, O:) or, in that instance,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Saf~FA", "text_ar": "صَفًّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "may mean"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "muSoTaf~iyna", "text_ar": "مُصْطَفِّينَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "standing in ranks"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], (Az, M, O,) as a denotative of state. (M.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A pair of bowls"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qadaHaAni", "text_ar": "قَدَحَانِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") [app., as seems to be indicated,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that are filled at one milking of a camel"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; because they are put together. (M.)       -A2-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A certain medicament with which the teeth are whitened."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O.)"}], "source_refs": ["M", "O", "K", "Az"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}